Package: capnet
Type: Package
Title: Contribution-Capped Elastic Net Model for Stable Feature Contributions
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-11-03
Authors@R: c(
    person("Harry", "He", email = "zih028@ucsd.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Petri", "Fast", role = c("aut"))
)
Description: Implements contribution-capped regularization to directly bound per-feature contributions in predictive models. Includes OWL-QN optimization, cross-validation, walk-forward fitting and prediction, and plotting utilities. 
